rComments: Boring Slides.  You can manage if you don't go to lecture.  The course was very fair and Prof Lian does her best to explain everything.
She has the worst slides, what is with the fill in the blank, and the textbook recommended for her class is useless.

Her lectures are always worth attending. She is very animated and enthusiastic while lecturing. Her tests aren't easy, but if you put in the effort and study with her slides and the text book you can do well.
